songs.title: Love or Drugs*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

[Verse]
[?] with the cannon I be spraying, yeah
But I can love no hoe (No)
Ain't let me go
And they don't even let me grow, I may come home (I may come home)
I can't take too much
Love, or drugs (Yeah, yeah, yeah)
Love, or lust (Yeah, yeah, yeah)
Hey, bush, [?], then I bail, yeah I'm out (Ooh)
Dick all in her mouth, cash all on the counter
Imma make her count
